Package org.apache.struts.webapp.validator

Class Summary
CityStateZip Just used to provide an indexed properties example.
EditTypeAction Initializes ActionForm.
LocaleAction Implementation of Action that changes the user's Locale and forwards to a page, based on request level parameters that are set (language, country, & page).
MultiRegistrationAction Implementation of Action that validates a multi-page registration form.
RegistrationAction Implementation of Action that validates a registration form.
RegistrationForm Form bean for the user registration page.
ShowFileAction Action which retrieves a file specified in the parameter and stores its contents in the request, so that they can be displayed.
TypeAction Implementation of Action that validates a different 'types'.
TypeForm Form bean for the user type page.
